---- Text Manipulation ----
i insert before cursor
I Insert at start of line

a insert after cursor
A insert at end of line 

o add new below cursor
O add new line above  cursor

ea insert at the end of line 

Esc exit


---------------------------------------------


---- Text Manipulation ----
y yank/copy
yy yank a line
yw yank a word
y$ yank to end of line 
p paste after cursor
P paste after cursor
dd delete/ cut a line
dw delete a word


----------------------------------------------

--- Visual Mode ---
v enter visual mode
V enter linewise visual mode
Ctrl start visual block mode 
> shift text left  
< shift text Right

>> shift left by shiftwidth
<< shift right by shiftwidth

== auto-indent line 


-----------------------------------------------

--- save and exit ---
ZZ save and quit
ZQ quit without saving
:w write/save
:q quit (fails if there are chnages)
:wq write and quite
:x write and quite
:q! force quit without saving
:q quit all vim buffer         



























